front end designing

1)create a project - ng new projectname
2)Run Angular  - ng s -o
3)Add bootstrap,fontawsome,google font
4)Lazy loading 
     its a procces of loading components and modules
     it improves application loading time and perfomance

     ng g m products --route products  --module app.module

 5)App router-outlet selector into the route component - app.component.html    

6)create a component should lazy loaded in this products module

-all-products - ng g c products/all-products
-cart - ng g c products/cart
-wishlist - ng g c products/wishlist

7)Setup path for each module
products-routing module

8)page not found - ng g c page not found - app.router module


9)Create header and footer

10)disgning of front end

11)Integration
  a)creating services for api calling- ng g s products/api
  b)import HttpClientModule in product module
  c)Dependency injection HttpClient class in API  serveses

12) page designing

13)search for a product
         ng g p products/pipes/filter
  
 
